text: Jakub Kudlička (born 10 January 1999) is a Slovak football midfielder who currently plays for Fortuna Liga club MFK Ružomberok. ==Club career== ===MFK Ružomberok=== Kudlička made his professional Fortuna Liga debut for MFK RužomberokRUŽOMBEROK VS.
